{"id":10622,"date":"2020-01-20T10:13:30","date_gmt":"2020-01-20T10:13:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/?p=10622"},"modified":"2020-03-16T10:14:54","modified_gmt":"2020-03-16T10:14:54","slug":"meet-up-armelle-sitchoma","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/meet-up-armelle-sitchoma\/","title":{"rendered":"Meet Up: Armelle Sitchoma"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p> Un \u00e9change a eu lieu jentre Armelle Sitchoma notre boursi\u00e8re du <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/hashtag\/factsmatter237?__cft__[0]=AZWpdp54L4q1ISiMEFS2nguFCSWqmkDEoV6jLfkV6k_0SDepduC4hb8l_-i8_XxM0mxfS1Rk3fj9u3UeHKMGTUi-W4_BqPC630LgEXIwnZ_9p8EBuyzIIr0d_FXrOyATdRtLipxCA-oMW70YjFVlceLFa7DDKJMaHK4S7jkFVICjPg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#FactsMatter237<\/a> et le personnel de la d\u00e9l\u00e9gation regionale de la Communication pour le Littoral.Ils ont \u00e9chang\u00e9 sur leur perception, l\u2019impact et la gestion du discours de la haine sur les r\u00e9seaux sociaux. Une pr\u00e9sentation du projet <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/hashtag\/defyhatenow?__cft__[0]=AZWpdp54L4q1ISiMEFS2nguFCSWqmkDEoV6jLfkV6k_0SDepduC4hb8l_-i8_XxM0mxfS1Rk3fj9u3UeHKMGTUi-W4_BqPC630LgEXIwnZ_9p8EBuyzIIr0d_FXrOyATdRtLipxCA-oMW70YjFVlceLFa7DDKJMaHK4S7jkFVICjPg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#defyhatenow<\/a> a \u00e9t\u00e9 faite par Armelle Sitchoma. Par la suite,ils ont \u00e9chang\u00e9 sur la mont\u00e9 du discours de la haine et des <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/hashtag\/fakenews?__cft__[0]=AZWpdp54L4q1ISiMEFS2nguFCSWqmkDEoV6jLfkV6k_0SDepduC4hb8l_-i8_XxM0mxfS1Rk3fj9u3UeHKMGTUi-W4_BqPC630LgEXIwnZ_9p8EBuyzIIr0d_FXrOyATdRtLipxCA-oMW70YjFVlceLFa7DDKJMaHK4S7jkFVICjPg&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#FakeNews<\/a> en ligne et son impact sur le terrain. Apr\u00e8s s&#8217;en est suivi des partages des exp\u00e9riences personnelles des uns et des autres avec ces fl\u00e9aux.  Il en ressort que le discours de la haine et la propagation des fakenews prennent de l\u2019ampleur au Cameroun.Il est imp\u00e9ratif de former les populations \u00e0 la citoyennet\u00e9 et au bon usage des r\u00e9seaux sociaux \u00e0 travers des \u00e9mission dans les m\u00e9dias traditionnels et les nouveaux m\u00e9dias. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1030\" height=\"773\" src=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o-1030x773.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10624\" srcset=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o-1030x773.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o-744x558.jpg 744w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o-1500x1125.jpg 1500w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o-705x529.jpg 705w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89137862_2651898241755563_7047398990312112128_o.jpg 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1030px) 100vw, 1030px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1030\" height=\"773\" src=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89351591_2651899671755420_4364861785593872384_o-1030x773.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-10625\" srcset=\"https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89351591_2651899671755420_4364861785593872384_o-1030x773.jpg 1030w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89351591_2651899671755420_4364861785593872384_o-744x558.jpg 744w, https:\/\/defyhatenow.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/89351591_26